data.description: Nestled within the highly sought-after Valley Center school district, this timeless  home exudes enduring charm while offering modern-day comfort. Featuring four bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms, it's a spacious haven for families and those who appreciate room to grow. The two-car garage, thoughtfully equipped with an oil changing pit, is a nod to the past while providing practicality for today's homeowner.  A brand new roof and a HVAC system ensure peace of mind and efficiency, allowing you to move in with confidence. But it's not just the modern upgrades that make this property special; it's the captivating charm of yesteryear. The grand staircase, an architectural masterpiece, welcomes you with open arms, leading you through a home where timeless elegance and contemporary living coexist harmoniously.  Whether you're enjoying the classic details or reveling in the updated features, this home beautifully encapsulates the best of both worlds, offering a unique and inviting ambiance that's ready for you to call it your own. It's a rare opportunity to embrace the allure of an older home without sacrificing the conveniences of modern living.
